data.description: This charming cul-de-sac home is located in the lovely neighborhood of NorthWest crossing. Upon entering, you will find a large living and dining room along with a kitchen that provides plenty of counter space and storage. The bedrooms are located towards the back of home, providing privacy and comfort. The master bathroom features a walk in shower. This home is settled on a .12 acre (5,227 square feet) lot.. Come make this house your home.
